summary: Thor: Ragnarok (2017) is incredible. It takes place on Asgard, Sakarr, and a little bit in Doctor Strange’s home. It’s got the...
caption:
Thor: Ragnarok (2017) is incredible. It takes place on Asgard, Sakarr, and a little bit in Doctor Strange’s home. It’s got the most psychedelic effects. It’s just the most beautiful, fun Marvel film. There are so many great sequences like the bit with Doctor Strange, Valkyrie’s memory of fighting Hela, the “Willy Wonka” presentation about the Grandmaster.

The characters are so good. Thor, Loki, Hela, Valkyrie, Hulk, Banner, the Grandmaster, Korg. They’re all so awesome, and it’s exciting to see them in a film that truly breaks the conventions of a superhero film to do its own thing.
